Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.67,0:01:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類因人口膨脹而向宇宙移民已過了半個世紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.26,0:01:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球周圍漂浮著巨大的人工都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.71,0:01:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為人類的「第二故鄉」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.37,0:01:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們就在這裏出生、成長、生兒育女\N並走向死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世紀0079年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.91,0:02:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離地球最遠的宇宙都市SIDE 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.43,0:02:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以ZION公國之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.57,0:02:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向地球聯邦政府發起了獨立戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.13,0:02:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在開始一個月的戰鬥裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.35,0:02:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公國和地球聯邦軍有半數以上的人口死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.23,0:02:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們對於自己的行為產生了恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.93,0:02:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『荒野是戰場』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.22,0:02:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！快撞山了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.93,0:03:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在副機艙裏面嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.37,0:03:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小寶，你是男子漢來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可以震盪一下便哭起來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，這裏是地球！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.32,0:03:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亦是你爸爸生長出世的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.79,0:03:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸爸是很偉大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.36,0:03:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很值得你驕傲的好爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是否所有的母親也是一樣的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.43,0:03:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你有很久未見過媽媽呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.67,0:03:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.97,0:03:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，隊長找你啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.94,0:03:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝！哈囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們真是胡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.55,0:03:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何不提高高度呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看不到敵機正在跟蹤著嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以的話，我簡直想在地上跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.89,0:04:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但起碼可以找別人駕駛呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做得來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.73,0:04:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是偵察機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.03,0:04:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木馬正越過山脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.14,0:04:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別讓他們飛過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.14,0:04:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快和地面的坦克聯絡一起進攻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.38,0:04:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.04,0:04:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了，夏亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.04,0:04:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道那母艦為何作這樣的航行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是想避過雷達跟蹤...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.72,0:04:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是想利用山脈來做防護網
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反過來展開防衛罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.96,0:04:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便是這樣，即是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.96,0:04:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏的粒子效果是絕大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.96,0:04:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好的追蹤器也使用不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.80,0:04:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,埋伏等他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.13,0:04:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找一處最有利的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.87,0:04:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後來一次總攻擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.87,0:04:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何他們的戰機會撤退呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.68,0:05:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定有原因的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.81,0:05:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們現在大峽谷地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而母艦的位置在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.25,0:05:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而敵人是想在湖邊處攻擊我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有同感！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.72,0:05:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以這裏是最不利的地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.63,0:05:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次的作戰戰果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.03,0:05:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就要全靠GUNDAM了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.66,0:05:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，拜託了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.36,0:05:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說我們無關重要啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.74,0:05:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.30,0:05:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波，他們想怎樣呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.44,0:05:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長，他們該無論如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.84,0:05:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要和你相討一下的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.85,0:05:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你可以給我離開！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.08,0:05:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！在這裏離艦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.79,0:05:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在仍是備戰狀態啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.69,0:05:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前面有處地方叫聖喬治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.16,0:05:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我丈夫的故鄉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.93,0:05:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故鄉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏很難聽到這名詞的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.86,0:05:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白你們是有難處的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我還是想帶我的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回鄉下長大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.47,0:06:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這班人實在太自私了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.97,0:06:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.89,0:06:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.61,0:06:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想到一個辦法！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.58,0:06:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辦法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.81,0:06:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！我向他們要求暫時停戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.21,0:06:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後讓他們下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.85,0:06:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.42,0:06:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認為如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.72,0:06:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們以難民離艦為理由宣佈停戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.33,0:06:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎是陰謀呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.09,0:06:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.33,0:06:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然不知這是什麼用意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但可以拖延一下時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.80,0:06:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.17,0:06:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行動較慢的陸戰武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.94,0:06:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便可以進行補給
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.74,0:06:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以戰勝的比率也較高了，對嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.31,0:06:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.64,0:06:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他這種少爺脾性真是單純
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.78,0:06:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真天真！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.36,0:06:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要炸毀它？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太可惜了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別吵了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.43,0:07:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們說不炸開一個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.83,0:07:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人是不會中計的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.96,0:07:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次一定會嬴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.73,0:07:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣也失敗就太低能了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這飛機不會回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.03,0:08:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不後悔嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早已下定了決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.64,0:08:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論怎樣也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.17,0:08:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要在地球撫養他成人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.37,0:08:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這種心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.41,0:08:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概你是不會明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.11,0:08:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我未在地球生活過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.15,0:08:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們來了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我們預測一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.27,0:08:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是約翰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.74,0:08:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已確定White Base的運輸機位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.07,0:08:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可疑嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.51,0:08:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機尾位置有中彈跡象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.04,0:08:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些跟班飛機又來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.41,0:08:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hi！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.80,0:08:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別亂來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.98,0:09:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你妒忌嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰妒忌呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.68,0:09:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是擔心計劃會失敗而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.72,0:09:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小孩和我們揮手啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.13,0:09:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我印象中好像從沒有個這麼大的一個湖在這裏...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.28,0:09:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那湖叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.95,0:09:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎是被大型炸彈炸出來的呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.45,0:09:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏降落吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.85,0:09:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏可看到四周
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.75,0:09:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降落這裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.99,0:09:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏有可居住的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.09,0:09:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在這附近降落吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.63,0:09:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.72,0:09:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始行動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.16,0:09:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.00,0:09:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就快可以了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.71,0:09:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，好像在燃燒呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！你們沒事吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.04,0:10:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來飛機故障了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是你們不好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.55,0:10:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要緊急降落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.44,0:10:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.15,0:10:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總部通話，我是約翰...總部！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.29,0:10:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來作留下的故障發作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.79,0:10:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們的運氣很差呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫他們繼續監視行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.53,0:10:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.73,0:10:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點不對呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.52,0:10:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.49,0:10:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,約定的地點到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.73,0:10:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能我過敏吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.53,0:10:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們正降低高度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.64,0:10:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要完成緊急降落，知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是了，我知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.74,0:11:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣子作戰我就最喜歡了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.74,0:11:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們會上當嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老人四個、女人兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.42,0:11:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩三個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.85,0:11:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一共是九個難民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.16,0:11:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎不在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.59,0:11:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.52,0:11:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為會有軍人偷走呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在監視他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.56,0:11:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那有可能走得掉呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.97,0:11:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說得沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.34,0:11:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們先住到那面的民居去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.47,0:11:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是一定要去聖喬治嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.88,0:11:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為路程不會太遠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.21,0:11:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但假苦找不到的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.58,0:11:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想會回來麻煩你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.46,0:11:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那對母子想去那裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.39,0:11:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再向前行也沒有民居吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.19,0:11:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！機長，你看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.93,0:12:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛員要離開，他們正飛向母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.13,0:12:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要跟著去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.61,0:12:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，我們成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.97,0:12:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵軍已中計！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.57,0:13:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘻，你看...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.58,0:13:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照看是沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.14,0:13:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要轉回去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.51,0:13:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在擔心那對母子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會被司令罵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.82,0:13:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪上校還年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.68,0:13:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會瞭解我們這年齡的人的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.04,0:13:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你突然幹什麼，良！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那偵察機又回來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.70,0:13:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.78,0:13:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他要去那裏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.71,0:13:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良 快打開艙門吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.97,0:14:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了！阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你先躲在湖裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.64,0:14:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待敵人進攻後便來個突襲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.64,0:14:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！你去那裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別用無線電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.25,0:14:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才偵察機是向著那對母子飛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.82,0:14:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有點不放心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.23,0:14:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.79,0:14:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切順利嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.89,0:14:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.82,0:14:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過15分鐘後就知道成不成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了！凱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.09,0:14:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有膽去試一試嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.63,0:14:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經對那地形掌握了個大概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.93,0:14:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該沒問題的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼坦克，鋼加農
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.23,0:14:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始準備！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.39,0:14:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.18,0:15:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你們，救我的兒子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.28,0:15:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.04,0:15:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別發現我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.18,0:15:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.78,0:15:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們再去查看一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.45,0:15:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先打開準備安全鎖！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.12,0:15:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟！被發現了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是聯邦軍的機動戰士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.77,0:15:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不發現我就可以沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備降落湖邊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.42,0:16:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.26,0:16:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和約翰失去了聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼一回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.53,0:16:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別理那偵察機，開始戰鬥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.55,0:16:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可否將高度降低！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.35,0:16:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太低的話母艦會撞向地面的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.79,0:16:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油！凱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好一試了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.60,0:17:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到地面了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.24,0:17:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被瞄準著！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.94,0:17:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...我不怕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看！在湖邊處的運輸機那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.74,0:17:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有個機動戰士出來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.05,0:17:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掩護我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.36,0:18:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒子彈？...糟了...用盡了子彈...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我軍現在是背著湖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.93,0:18:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面向敵軍的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.37,0:18:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.47,0:18:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坦克部隊向前挺進了三公哩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.70,0:18:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪！吩咐背著湖的機槍及坦克部隊向前！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.67,0:18:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.88,0:18:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想那艘母艦捱不了多久呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.65,0:18:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在湖邊的運輸機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.35,0:18:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會有敵軍機動戰士出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.88,0:18:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我的話一定會這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.49,0:18:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們並沒有檢查過那一輛運輸機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.05,0:18:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在岩石後面有機動戰士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.46,0:18:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真...真的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.89,0:18:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦？沒可能的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.97,0:18:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是GUNDAM來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.57,0:18:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,計劃順利進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.04,0:18:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM正在敵軍背面攻擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.94,0:18:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！火力集中在前面！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.85,0:18:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.55,0:18:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要將前面的馬傑拉戰車全部炸毀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.91,0:19:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣死人！打中自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.78,0:19:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.76,0:19:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒走得那麼容易！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知那方戰況如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.28,0:20:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.48,0:20:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭的勝負是難以估計的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.68,0:20:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論誰會勝出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.55,0:20:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也會有很多女人像我般的不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.76,0:20:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人沒了丈夫是很悲慘的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.36,0:20:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小寶，你睡著了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.14,0:20:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算GUNDAM如何利害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那麼多敵人包圍下也會輸的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.47,0:20:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼小的事，我也可以做得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.00,0:21:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人的新機動戰士！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.35,0:21:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後兩台ZAKU被炸毀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.05,0:21:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總部，怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.02,0:21:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的馬傑拉戰車部隊已全滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有任何可動的戰車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.53,0:21:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撤退，撤退啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.66,0:21:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了..今次的損失慘重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.03,0:21:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我如何向基西莉亞姐姐交待呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.17,0:21:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有機會挽回局面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.70,0:21:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.64,0:21:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指揮官一定要在前線才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.17,0:21:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次我也要參加作戰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.11,0:21:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多謝你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.31,0:21:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要返回基地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.25,0:21:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想今晚你們最好睡在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.42,0:21:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我投下來的膠囊裏吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.52,0:21:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你們的幫忙呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.89,0:21:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小弟弟，你要堅強些保護母親啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.09,0:21:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.57,0:22:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太太！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.93,0:22:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.60,0:22:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得這裏以前是叫做聖喬治的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.27,0:22:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照看你還是回去湖邊那班同伴處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.14,0:22:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會比較好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.91,0:22:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？這裏就是...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.68,0:22:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏就是...聖喬治...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.56,0:22:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.91,0:22:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽！
